    "description": "Discipline: Waijia\nSkill: Light Melee against Parry\nType: Normal\nQi: 1\n\nYou lash out with your fly-whisk, its tethers extending unnaturally long to reach opponents and pull them closer. Roll Light Melee against Parry. On a Success you can extend the lash of your fly-whisk to wrap around foes or disarm them at a distance (10 feet per Rank of Qi). Anyone struck can be pulled to you that round (though they can make a Muscle roll against your Attack result to get away). Cathartic: When used Cathartically you can throw your opponent causing 1d10 falling Damage per Rank of Waijia.",
